             When an immense mining ship, the USG Ishimura, comes into contact with
             a mysterious alien artifact in a remote
             star system, its communications with Earth are mysteriously cut off. 
             Engineer Isaac Clarke is sent to repair the Ishimura's communications 
             array, but he arrives to find a living nightmareГ№the ship is a 
             floating bloodbath, the crew unspeakably mutilated and infected by 
             an ancient alien scourge. Clarke's repair mission becomes one of 
             survival as he fights not just to save himself, but to return the artifact
             to the planet Г  at any cost.

                          
